abstract: Sara Takanashi wins ski jumping World Cup event in Oslo.

headline.main: Sara Takanashi Extends Her Streak in Ski Jumping

snippet: Sara Takanashi soared in Oslo to her eighth straight ski jumping World Cup win, extending her lead in the overall standings.
lead_paragraph: Sara Takanashi soared in Oslo to her eighth straight ski jumping World Cup win, extending her lead in the overall standings.
